parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden stalling of the engine can cause loss of control, accidents, and leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls while driving
often without warning
and may not restart immediately. The dashboard lights may come on
and the engine may make unusual noises.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking of the engine cylinder bore liner can cause engine failure, leading to loss of control, accidents, and strandings.
symptoms: The engine may make unusual noises
perform poorly
or stall. The vehicle may not restart after stalling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the AWD system can cause loss of control, accidents, and strandings, especially in inclement weather conditions.
symptoms: The AWD system may not engage properly
causing the vehicle to lose traction or become stuck.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The overheating of the heater core can cause burns, and the failure of the cooling system can lead to engine damage.
symptoms: The heater core may become extremely hot
causing burns
and the cooling system may fail
leading to engine overheating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to loss of control, accidents, and strandings.
symptoms: The vehicle may stall or lose power
and the dashboard lights may come on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The transmission shifts hard between gears
vibrates
or shudders; the vehicle stalls or loses power; the transmission fails to engage or disengage properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: AWD system failure can cause the vehicle to lose traction, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The AWD system engages or disengages improperly
causing the vehicle to vibrate
shudder
or lose traction; the vehicle fishtails or spins out; the AWD system fails to engage in snowy or icy conditions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Differential failure can cause the vehicle to lose power or control, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The differential locks up or fails to engage properly
causing the vehicle to vibrate or lose traction; the differential makes a loud noise or grinding sound.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transfer case failure can cause the vehicle to lose power or control, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The transfer case fails to engage or disengage properly
causing the vehicle to vibrate or lose traction; the transfer case makes a loud noise or grinding sound.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: PCM failure can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power; the PCM fails to communicate with other systems
causing the vehicle to malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, and shut down, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or shuts down while driving
loss of power
instrument cluster panel lights go dark
unable to read mileage
fuel level
etc.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The stalling and loss of power can cause the vehicle to lose control, increasing the risk of accidents, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power while driving
often without warning
and may require towing or restarting after a period of time.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the instrument panel cluster can cause the driver to lose vital information, such as speed, fuel level, and mileage, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The instrument panel cluster lights go dark
or the gauges fail to function
making it difficult for the driver to operate the vehicle safely.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The seat heater fire can cause damage to the vehicle and increase the risk of injury or death to occupants.
symptoms: The seat heater catches fire
often without warning
and can spread to other parts of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power and control, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The transmission fails
causing the vehicle to stall or lose power
and may require repair or replacement.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall or shut down, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The ignition switch fails
causing the vehicle to stall or shut down
often without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the all-wheel drive system can cause the vehicle to lose traction and control, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The all-wheel drive system engages and disengages erratically
causing the vehicle to lose traction and control.
